{"tid":2389718,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"隔牆有耳：陳健民周五做「見山」店長（李八方）","createTime":"2021-02-01T05:47:56.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-01T05:47:56.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"b97023f7a5ba4ae4fb4cc6ec24732fee1fec391a","tid":2389718,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T05:47:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210201/XK2E572SKNCFFD5HXUB6U62BDM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210201%2FXK2E572SKNCFFD5HXUB6U62BDM%2F&d=NiOc6rc%2FE9fikVhzT7%2F1G%2FFBXrQbHxe6tNmRytRnjp4%3D&h=2541b1fe\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210201%2FXK2E572SKNCFFD5HXUB6U62BDM%2F&h=911d3ea1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210201/XK2E572SKNCFFD5HXUB6U62BDM/</a><br />\n<br />\n隔牆有耳：陳健民周五做「見山」店長（李八方）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/jJCYklYAvNC_MZyCQeEEBKlO4qM=/886x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/HNUSGFBB6JBEBD75OUZ45D2GOA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FjJCYklYAvNC_MZyCQeEEBKlO4qM%3D%2F886x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FHNUSGFBB6JBEBD75OUZ45D2GOA.jpg&h=7da00077&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■陳健民喺fb預告本周五到見山書店做一日店長兼向大家推薦好書。<br />\n<br />\n佔中三子之一嘅陳健民（KM）去年出獄後，積極開拓網上平台，除開設「KM Chan健民書房」YouTube頻道，亦整咗「健民講堂」民主教育平台，繼續為香港民主運動發聲。早前出版《陳健民獄中書簡》嘅KM，嚟緊又有新搞作，就係到書店任店長！<br />\n<br />\nKM喺fb透露，佢會喺本周五中午12點至下晝6點，到見山書店（上環太平山街6C）做一日店長，當日除咗收錢，仲會向大家推薦店內好書，相信大家都好想知，KM有乜私心推介。<br />\n<br />\n至於之前撲唔到KM新書嘅讀者，亦有好消息，皆因當日KM會有少量《陳健民獄中書簡》簽名本發售。一早已買咗書嘅朋友，亦可帶埋《書簡》去搵KM簽名同傾偈。想喺現時北風凜冽嘅香港圍一圍爐，周五不妨動身暖一暖！<br />\n<br />\n李八方"}]}